msgid ""
"Tiered Pricing for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to be installed and "
"active."
msgstr ""

#. Plugin Name of the plugin/theme
msgid "Tiered Pricing for WooCommerce"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"Offer tiered, quantity-based pricing on WooCommerce products. Automatically "
"adjusts the per-unit price as customers increase quantity — for example: "
"$5.00 each for 10 units, $4.00 each for 30 units. Supports unlimited "
"pricing tiers per product."
msgstr ""

